#ROOM
Vnum     11800
Name     &CThe City Gates of Darnassus&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand before the majestic, open-air gates of the Kaldorei capital.
The architecture is seamlessly blended with the towering, ancient trees
of Teldrassil. The air here is cool, still, and smells of blooming
moonweeds. To the north lies the heart of the city.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11801
Desc      A pristine marble bridge leads into the city.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11800 2 11800
  Reset E 1 11800 10 16
  Reset E 1 11803 10 5
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11801
Name     &CThe Tradesmen's Terrace - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The bridge from the gates opens up into a serene, circular terrace
built over a crystal-clear lake. Glowing wisps dart among the branches
above. To the east is the city's Bank, and to the west is the Auction
House.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11804
Desc      The path winds toward the Craftsmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11803
Desc      The Darnassus Bank.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11800
Desc      The city gates.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11802
Desc      The Darnassus Auction House.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11813 3 11801
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11802
Name     &CThe Darnassus Auction House&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Unlike the chaotic trading floors of the other capitals, the auction
house of Darnassus operates in hushed, polite tones. Night elves and
visiting Alliance members quietly inspect magical goods and rare herbs
under the soft light of the moon.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11801
Desc      The Tradesmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11803 1 11802
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11803
Name     &CThe Darnassus Bank&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This grand structure is carved directly out of the living wood of an
immense ancient tree. Roots naturally form secure vaults and lockboxes.
Banker Ulthir stands watch, relying on ancient magic to secure the
treasures within.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11801
Desc      The Tradesmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11804 1 11803
  Reset E 1 11800 10 16
Reset O 0 11809 3 11803
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11804
Name     &CThe Craftsmen's Terrace&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     This terrace is dedicated to the peaceful arts. The sounds of gentle
hammering and the smell of cooking food fill the air. To the north
lies a welcoming inn, its hearth glowing warmly through the open arches.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11805
Desc      The local Inn.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11806
Desc      A path over a bubbling stream.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11801
Desc      The Tradesmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11807
Desc      The Warrior's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11805
Name     &CDarnassus Inn&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The inn is open and airy, built entirely of polished wood without a
single nail. Soft, moss-covered beds provide incredible comfort to weary
travelers. Innkeeper Saelienne hums a quiet elven tune as she works.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11804
Desc      The Craftsmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11805 1 11805
Reset O 0 11805 2 11805
Reset O 0 11806 3 11805
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11806
Name     &CBridge to the Temple&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     An elegant, arching bridge spans the tranquil waters of the city's
central lake. To the east, the awe-inspiring architecture of the
Temple of the Moon begins to rise above the treeline.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11812
Desc      The Temple Gardens.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
