#ROOM
Vnum     11807
Name     &CThe Warrior's Terrace - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The serene atmosphere of the city is contrasted here by the sharp sound
of clashing steel and the roar of tamed beasts. This district is where
the Sentinels and hunters of Darnassus hone their lethal skills.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11808
Desc      The Hunter's Enclave.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11804
Desc      The Craftsmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
