Reset M 0 11800 2 11807
  Reset E 1 11800 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11808
Name     &CHunter's Enclave&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Massive nightsabers rest in the cool grass, watching you with intelligent,
predatory eyes. Hunters practice their archery on targets set deep into
the woods.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11807
Desc      The entrance of the terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11809
