  Reset E 1 11801 10 3
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11809
Name     &CTracking Grounds&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Erion Shadewhisper stands here, analyzing the footprints left in the
soft earth. This area is used to teach young night elves how to move
without leaving a trace and how to survive in the deep wilds.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11808
Desc      The Hunter's Enclave.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11807 1 11809
  Reset E 1 11807 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11810
Name     &CWarrior's Training Ring&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The grass here is worn down from centuries of combat practice. Darnath
Bladesinger guides initiates through fluid, deadly combat forms, teaching
them that agility and precision will always overcome brute strength.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11807
Desc      The entrance of the terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11811
Desc      A dark, shadowed alcove.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11811 1 11810
  Reset E 1 11800 10 16
  Reset E 1 11814 10 11
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11811
Name     &CThe Shadowed Alcove&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    dark~
Desc     The canopy is incredibly thick here, plunging the area into perpetual
twilight. The rogues of Darnassus train here, mastering the arts of
stealth, sabotage, and assassination in service to the Goddess.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11810
Desc      The training ring.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11808 1 11811
  Reset E 1 11813 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11812
Name     &CTemple Gardens&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You have crossed the bridge into the holiest district in the city. The
Temple Gardens are perfectly manicured, glowing with a soft, ethereal
light that seems to emanate from the plants themselves.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11813
Desc      The grand steps of the Temple.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11806
