~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11813
Name     &CTemple of the Moon - Grand Steps&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A massive flight of marble stairs leads up into the awe-inspiring Temple
of the Moon. The architecture is breathtaking, completely open to the
sky to allow the moonlight to bathe the interior at night.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11814
Desc      The entrance hall of the Temple.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
