#ROOM
Vnum     11814
Name     &CTemple of the Moon - Entrance Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand within the great Temple. The silence here is profound and deeply
comforting. The air is perfectly still. To the east lies the central
moonwell and the High Priestess herself.
~
