#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11816
Name     &CTemple of the Moon - Eastern Balcony&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     This open-air balcony provides a stunning view of the vast, mystical
forests of Teldrassil. The wind sighs softly through the marble pillars,
carrying the scent of pine.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11815
Desc      The central moonwell.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11817
Name     &CPriest's Quarters&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The acolytes and priestesses of Elune study ancient scrolls and practice
their healing prayers here. The atmosphere is one of absolute devotion
and unwavering faith in the Goddess.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11815
Desc      The central moonwell.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11809 1 11817
  Reset E 1 11802 10 5
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11818
Name     &CThe Northern Bridges&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You leave the Craftsmen's Terrace and head north over a series of elegant
wooden bridges that span the city's waterways. The magic in the air grows
wilder and more untamed as you approach the Cenarion Enclave.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11819
Desc      The Cenarion Enclave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11804
Desc      The Craftsmen's Terrace.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11819
Name     &GCenarion Enclave - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The pristine marble of the city gives way entirely to untamed, vibrant
nature. The Cenarion Enclave is the domain of the druids, a lush,
overgrown sanctuary of ancient trees, deep moss, and powerful earth magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11820
Desc      The heart of the enclave.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11818
Desc      The bridges back to the city.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11813 3 11819
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11820
Name     &GCenarion Enclave - The Great Tree&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     An impossibly massive tree towers above you, its roots forming natural
pathways and dwellings. Druids in various animal forms wander peacefully
through the brush.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11821
Desc      The druidic training grounds.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11824
Desc      A path winding around the roots.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11819
Desc      The enclave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11825
Desc      The protector's grove.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11821
Name     &GDruidic Training Grounds&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The grass here is thick and soft. Initiates practice their shapeshifting,
learning to command the forms of the bear, the cat, and the aquatic
creatures of the world.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11822
Desc      The Archdruid's Rise.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11820
Desc      The Great Tree.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11823
Desc      The Sleeping Den.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11811 1 11821
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11822
Name     &GArchdruid's Rise&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A raised platform of living wood. Archdruid Fandral Staghelm paces here,
his expression severe. He commands the Cenarion Circle with an iron fist,
believing that the druids must take a more active, militant role.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11821
Desc      The training grounds.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11802 1 11822
  Reset E 1 11808 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11823
Name     &GThe Sleeping Den&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A dark, quiet hollow carved into the roots of a giant oak. Several druids
slumber deeply here, their spirits wandering the vast, untouched wilds
of the Emerald Dream.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11821
Desc      The training grounds.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11810 1 11823
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11824
Name     &GPath of Roots&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The pathway here is formed entirely by the massive, interwoven roots of
the great trees. Small, glowing flowers bloom wherever you step, a sign
of the deep natural magic permeating the enclave.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11820
Desc      The Great Tree.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11825
Name     &GProtector's Grove&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The trees here seem to watch you. Suddenly, one of the massive oaks shifts
its weight, revealing itself to be an Ancient of War. These colossal,
sentient trees guard the enclave from any who would harm the forest.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11820
Desc      The Great Tree.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11814 1 11825
  Reset E 1 11814 10 11
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11826
Name     &CPath to the Roost&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Leaving the enclave behind, this path slopes upward, winding its way
toward the highest branches of Darnassus. The air grows thinner, and
the squawks of large, winged beasts echo from above.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11827
Desc      The base of the roost.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11819
Desc      The Cenarion Enclave entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11827
Name     &CBase of the Hippogryph Roost&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the base of a towering wooden ramp that spirals upward into
the canopy. Feathers and scratches in the wood mark the frequent passage
of the city's favored flying mounts.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11828
Desc      Ascend to the roost.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11826
Desc      The path back down.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11810 2 11827
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11828
Name     &CDarnassus Hippogryph Roost&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are high above the city, standing on a wide wooden platform built into
the upper branches of a massive tree. Several majestic Hippogryphs rest
here. From this vantage point, you can see the edge of the world tree,
Teldrassil, dropping off into the ocean.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11827
Desc      The ramp down.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11829
Desc      A small observation deck.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11812 1 11828
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11829
Name     &CObservation Deck&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A small, quiet deck extending out from the main roost. It offers an
unparalleled, unobstructed view of the stars and the moon. Many Night
Elves come here simply to marvel at the beauty of Elune's light.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11828
Desc      The main roost.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ENDAREA

